msgctxt "body.9ead4ce8-7292-412f-8702-f6c2f38093dc.right_column.6a7f07fe-f474-46b5-bb76-75c4f023e03d"
msgid "Zeina Abi Assy is an award-winning curator, cultural producer, writer and designer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.9ead4ce8-7292-412f-8702-f6c2f38093dc.right_column.6a7f07fe-f474-46b5-bb76-75c4f023e03d"
msgid ""
"She is the Director of the Mozilla Festival, a global gathering that convenes technologists, activists, policymakers, artists, entrepreneurs and researchers to imagine and build more ethical, mutual"
" futures for AI and the internet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.9ead4ce8-7292-412f-8702-f6c2f38093dc.right_column.6a7f07fe-f474-46b5-bb76-75c4f023e03d"
msgid ""
"Previously, she was the Director of Interactive Programs at Tribeca Film Institute, where she co-curated Tribeca Film Festival’s Interactive Day and Immersive Exhibition, showcasing large-scale "
"installations and conversations at the intersection of emerging technology and storytelling. She has also consulted festivals and conferences across Europe and the SWANA region on themes related to "
"technology, storytelling and immersive media."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.9ead4ce8-7292-412f-8702-f6c2f38093dc.right_column.6a7f07fe-f474-46b5-bb76-75c4f023e03d"
msgid "Her writing has appeared in the printed anthologies <i>Arab Women Voice New Realities</i> and <i>We Call to the Eye &amp; the Night</i>."
msgstr ""
